high_descs: Go straight and slightly to the left to enter the kitchen area, stopping at the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn back the way you came and go to the dining table next to the counters.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Look towards the shorter end of the table towards the open path.
Place the knife down on the table.
Look back to the tomato you just sliced.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Walk around the table to get to the fridge in the corner of the kitchen.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn around and go to the microwave ahead.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato slice in a microwave.
